Package: weather.gov
Title: NWS Weather API Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the National Weather Service API. Covers forecasts,
    active alerts, and observation stations for US locations. Includes LLM context
    injection via nws_context().
